videos.headline: Daniels connects with McKitty for 6-yard Georgia TD
videos.description: JT Daniels throws to Tre' McKitty, who dives into the end zone for the first touchdown of his Georgia career.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Daniels connects with McKitty for 6-yard Georgia TD) 2020/11/28 ESHEET

videos.headline: Zamir White runs for 22-yard Georgia TD
videos.description: Zamir White goes untouched up the middle of the South Carolina defense for a 22-yard touchdown for Georgia.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Zamir White runs for 22-yard Georgia TD) 2020/11/28 ESHEET

videos.headline: Cook runs 29 yards for his second TD vs. South Carolina
